-- Germany Wants Reform Before Greece Gets Aid, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-02-23T18:08:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-23/germany-wants-reform-before-greece-gets-aid-handelsblatt-says.html
Germany ’s government doesn’t want
 Greece  to get any funds from its second bailout package until
the country has implemented the agreed structural reforms,
 Handelsblatt  newspaper reported in a preview of an article that
will be published tomorrow, citing a draft government document.  To contact the reporter on this story:
